  "instructions": [
    "heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add lemongrass and galangal from infuse oil and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "add garlic and ginger and cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "add chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add strawberries and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "pour in coconut milk and stir to combine.",
    "add fish sauce, palm sugar, turmeric, and cumin. Stir well.",
    "bring curry to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, or until chicken is cooked through.",
    "season with salt to taste.",
    "serve hot, garnished with fresh herbs, if desired"
